data.value: The Mercedes-Benz A-Class offers a diverse range of options, from the entry-level A180 models priced under $50,000 to the high-performance AMG A45 S, which commands around $100,000. Available in both sedan and hatch formats, the A-Class showcases Mercedes-Benz's commitment to luxury and innovation. The AMG A45 S is particularly impressive, boasting a powerful 310kW/500Nm engine and a blistering 3.9-second 0-100km/h sprint time. With a competitive drive rating of 8.6/10, the A-Class delivers on both performance and luxury. Safety is paramount, evidenced by its 5-star ANCAP safety rating from 2018, while the generous 5-year/unlimited km warranty provides peace of mind for owners. Fuel efficiency ranges from 6.5 to 8.9 L/100km, making it an economical choice for daily driving. Whether seeking comfort, style, or performance, the Mercedes-Benz A-Class offers a compelling package for discerning drivers, with prices ranging from $61,900 to $119,900.
